 处理器、16g 内存、512g 存储，京东买的，当初差不多 2 万块……</p>\n<p>现在想出也不知道去哪里出靠谱一些，爱回收可行吗？</p>\n<p>之前听群里小伙伴说，4000 块都不一定有人要这个垃圾……</p>\n<p>大家说现在英特尔的 MBP ，就是垃圾，傻逼才买……我只能看着说不出话……</p>\n<p>好羡慕用 M 系列处理器的老哥们，冰冰凉凉的，性能强，续航强……</p>\n<p>如果要换 32G 内存，1T 存储的话，请问 V 友们推荐的淘宝店：摩集</p>\n<p>这一家怎么样？有人买过吗？能在上面买不……</p>\n", "last_modified": 1687761439, "replies": 118, "id": 951781}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1677911181", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1677911181", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 56870, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1677911181", "stars": 8447, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 521444, "username": "vihv", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/vihv", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/dc02863bb7b5cfee336611689d104e1d?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/dc02863bb7b5cfee336611689d104e1d?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/dc02863bb7b5cfee336611689d104e1d?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1606774045, "last_modified": 1606774045}, "last_reply_by": "charlie21", "last_touched": 1687841035, "title": "成都的工资太低了吧", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/951799", "created": 1687765356, "deleted": 0, "content": "从上海来到成都，有三四年开发经验，有点被成都的招聘市场惊呆到，3-5 年经验的开发者，薪资 9-13k ，区间中间数是真实能给到的工资，11k 。\r\n\r\n在上海只要能胜任工作就行了，在成都他还要求我是个人才。\r\n\r\n纯吐槽一下，可能今年的就业环境就是这么艰难，个人面对这种情况是没有什么办法的，被打击几周之后，也许只能接受现实。", "content_rendered": "<p>从上海来到成都，有三四年开发经验，有点被成都的招聘市场惊呆到，3-5 年经验的开发者，薪资 9-13k ，区间中间数是真实能给到的工资，11k 。</p>\n<p>在上海只要能胜任工作就行了，在成都他还要求我是个人才。</p>\n<p>纯吐槽一下，可能今年的就业环境就是这么艰难，个人面对这种情况是没有什么办法的，被打击几周之后，也许只能接受现实。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1687765356, "replies": 97, "id": 951799}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1608969785", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1608969785", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 4523, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785", "stars": 1149, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 398672, "username": "HeHeDaGe", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/HeHeDaGe", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/28baa0fa27dda9ba8fd3ceff26a33e33?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/28baa0fa27dda9ba8fd3ceff26a33e33?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/28baa0fa27dda9ba8fd3ceff26a33e33?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1554374621, "last_modified": 1667796456}, "last_reply_by": "sinux", "last_touched": 1687842262, "title": "即将还完房贷，很激动", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/951849", "created": 1687772183, "deleted": 0, "content": "记录一下，准备下班跟媳妇吃顿好的，欧耶\\(^o^)/\r\n \r\n ![]( https://i.imgur.com/OPbrkqg.png)  \r\n ![]( https://i.imgur.com/zTKl7uK.png)  \r\n ![]( https://i.imgur.com/Dd0S2in.jpeg)", "content_rendered": "<p>记录一下，准备下班跟媳妇吃顿好的，欧耶(^o^)/</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/OPbrkqg.png\"/><br/>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zTKl7uK.png\"/><br/>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Dd0S2in.jpeg\"/></p>\n", "last_modified": 168777218